# Libs

sudo apt-get install cmake build-essential
sudo apt-get install libi2c-dev (for i2c bus communication)

# Install ROS in RPI

http://wiki.ros.org/ROSberryPi/Installing%20ROS%20Kinetic%20on%20the%20Raspberry%20Pi 
// Follow this to the character ! If it hangs during ros compilation (near package 41) hit Ctrl+C and re-compile with -j2.


# Configs

Go to raspi-config and enable SSH, SPI and I2C.

